        <h2>Ganuk</h2>
        <p>
            Ganuk is the son of Inukshuk and was born in captivity in Quebec on November 30, 2009. He moved to the Habitat in 2012. Ganuk is usually the heaviest bear at the Habitat usually weighing between 1,000-1,100 lbs. Ganuk likes to wander around and tends to stay inside when it starts to rain. Other than that and certain vegetables, Ganuk isn’t really picky.
