        <p>
            Inukshuk was born sometime during the Winter Season of 2002-2003 in the wild. At only a couple months old he was orphaned. He has fathered 5 cubs total (Ganuk, Hudson, Taiga, Juno, and Humphrey). He started living at the Habitat part-time in 2012 and has been living full time since 2016. He enjoys eating beaver unlike the other bears at the Habitat.
